### Books — List all books
# Requires: ROLE_MEMBER (member1 / member123)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books
Authorization: Basic bWVtYmVyMTptZW1iZXIxMjM=

###

### Books — Get book by ID
# Requires: ROLE_MEMBER (member1 / member123)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/50
Authorization: Basic bWVtYmVyMTptZW1iZXIxMjM=

###

### Books — Get reviews for a book
# Requires: ROLE_MEMBER (member1 / member123)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/50/reviews
Authorization: Basic bWVtYmVyMTptZW1iZXIxMjM=

###

### Books — Get books by genre
# genreId=1 → Science Fiction
# Requires: ROLE_MEMBER (member1 / member123)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books/by-genre/1
Authorization: Basic bWVtYmVyMTptZW1iZXIxMjM=

###

### Authors — List all authors
